---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NavBar from '../components/NavBar.astro';
import Twikoo from '../components/Twikoo.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于 - krya">
  <NavBar slot="header" />
  
  <div class="col-mb-12" id="main" role="main">
    <article class="post">
      <h1 class="post-title">关于我</h1>
      <div class="post-content">
		
        <p>你好，我是 Jin，居住在四川成都🐼。</p>

        <p>我主要从事互联网相关工作，有一个幸福的家庭（妻子和女儿）。业余时间喜欢旅行和探索新技术，写博客这件事从 2008 年坚持到现在，已经 17 年了。</p>

        <p>这个博客是我的私人旅行记录地，用来存放自驾游见闻和路上的风景。如果你也喜欢在路上，欢迎常来逛逛。</p>
		
		<h2>关于本博客</h2>
		
		<p>经历过百度空间、网易博客、WordPress、Blogger，2014 年转用 Typecho，2026 年正式采用 Astro 框架将博客静态化。本站主题由我自己设计，Hermes Agent 协助实现前端功能代码。</p>
		
		<p>文章存在家里的小 Linux 主机上，用 Obsidian 编辑，写完发给 Hermes，它帮我推送到 GitHub，然后云平台自动构建部署。整个过程不需要我手动操作——我喜欢把重复的事情交给机器。</p>
		
		<h2>About Me</h2>
		 
		<p>Hi, I'm Jin, based in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chengdu">Chengdu</a>, China 🐼.</p>

		<p>I work in the internet industry and have a lovely family. Since 2008, I've been maintaining this blog for over 17 years.</p>

		<p>This blog is a personal travel journal — a place where I keep my road trip logs, photos, and thoughts from the road. If you love traveling too, feel free to look around.</p>
		
		<h2>About This Blog</h2>
		
		<p>I've moved from Baidu Kongjian, Netease Blog, WordPress, and Blogger to Typecho in 2014, and finally to a static site built with Astro in 2026. I designed the theme myself, with Hermes Agent helping with the frontend code.</p>
        
		<h2>Contact:</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hi@krya.com">hi@krya.com</a> </p>
		<p>Twitter: <a href="https://x.com/uniifi">jin</a></p>
        
        <h2>版权声明</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise noted, all content on this site/this article is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a></p>
        <p>除另有注明外，本站/本文内容采用 知识共享署名 - 非商业性使用 - 相同方式共享 4.0 国际许可协议 (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0) 进行许可。</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    
    <Twikoo />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
